, saṅghassa ābhaṭaṃ bhattaṃ saṅghabhattaṃ, saṅghatthāya vā paṭiyattaṃ bhattaṃ saṅghabhattaṃ. Evaṃ āgantukabhattaṃ, gamikabhattaṃ, gilānabhattaṃ.

