Chāyā, sabhāsvevāyaṃ vidhi, salabhānaṃ chāyā salabhacchāyaṃ…sabhacchāyaṃ 
Note { id=55, line='202', referenceLine='309', original='…sabhacchāyaṃ (mūlapāṭhe)', type='auto', previous='Chāyā, sabhāsvevāyaṃ vidhi, salabhānaṃ chāyā salabhacchāyaṃ '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='salabhacchāyaṃ'}
	Alternative{lang='mūlapāṭhe', text='…sabhacchāyaṃ'}}
. Evaṃ sakaṭacchāyaṃ, gharacchāyaṃ. Idha na hoti, rukkhacchāyā, pabbatacchāyā. Sabhāsadde amanussasabhāsvevāyaṃ vidhi, brahmūnaṃ sabhā brahmasabhaṃ. Evaṃ devasabhaṃ, indasabhaṃ, yakkhasabhaṃ, rakkhasasataṃ. Manussasabhāsu natthi, khattiyasabhā, rājasabhā iccādi.

